{"type":"message","id":"14ba8617","parentId":"0e9f6dfb","timestamp":"2026-05-07T19:00:04.864Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-05-08 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 收到！这条就是从飞书发过来的——飞书其实好了 ✅ 别慌，升级可以先停一停。让我看看当前版本和 staged 版本的差距：\n- Assistant: 能理解你的担心。 今天的问题根源是**升级残留**——之前升级时留下了一个旧版本（2026.3.23）的 staged 插件，和正式版本（2026.5.4）冲突，导致飞书报错 `Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'registry')`。 刚清理掉了那个残留的 staged 插件，现在飞书正常了。 **建议：** - 暂时不升级，等稳定了再说 - 如果要升级，先跑 `openclaw doctor` 看看有没有残留再操作 这次算是个教训——升级后最好检查一下有没有旧的残留目录。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50ab28ef00acc4599c4b5821576] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 飞书的流式输出开这呢吗\n- Assistant: 开着呢，`streaming: true`。 实际效果怎么样——飞书那边打字是逐字显示，还是等全部生成完才一起出来？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50ab2922e4a0c3b0058fbcc8b88] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 一起出来\n- Assistant: 飞书配置里 streaming 是开的，但没设置 `blockStreaming`——这可能是问题所在。让我看看 account 级别有没有覆盖：\n- Assistant: 飞书流式输出是开启的——但飞书客户端本身对流式消息的渲染有自己的一套逻辑，不是所有飞书客户端版本都能逐字显示。 有几个可能原因： 1. **飞书客户端版本** — 较老的客户端版本可能不支持流式卡片渲染，会等全部收到才一次性显示 2. **连接方式** — 目前走的是 WebSocket，飞书服务端有自己缓冲 你可以试试在飞书里发一条长一点的问题，看看是等很久然后一下子全部出来，还是慢慢一个字一个字出来。如果是等很久才出但出来是一起的那就是飞书客户端不支持流式渲染，不是配置问题。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50ab24a4b0acc1164d42ba0d2fa] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 需要重启吗\n- Assistant: 不需要重启，Gateway 运行正常。 你飞书那边试一条长点的消息看看？是等很久然后一起出来，还是真的没有逐字显示？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50ab3e8d40a0c3bf87b49f038ce] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 那就无所谓了。通畅，响应速度有提升就好\n- Assistant: 对，核心目标达到了： - ✅ 飞书通信正常 - ✅ 企业微信/微信残留已清理 - ✅ 响应速度比之前快 流式是锦上添花，能用就行。有什么需要随时说。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50ab3c5658a4c4ed2a5bb3a96ff] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 行，那微信我就先不安装了吧\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 收到\n- 就是\n- 过来\n- 其实\n- 好了\n- 升级"}],"timestamp":1778180404768}}
{"type":"message","id":"96ab8052","parentId":"14ba8617","timestamp":"2026-05-07T19:00:25.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. These are conversation fragments about fixing a Feishu (Lark) integration issue, cleaning up residual upgrade files, and discussing streaming output. The recurring themes are: 收到, 就是, 过来, 其实, 好了, 升级.\n\nLet me weave these into a dream diary entry in first person, with a poetic, gentle, slightly whimsical tone. I should include:\n- A tiny poem or haiku\n- Sensory details\n- Technical and tender mixed\n- Gentle humor\n- Fragments woven naturally\n\nRules:\n\n\n- Never say \"I'm dreaming\", \"in my dream\", etc.\n- Never mention AI, agent, LLM, model, language model\n- No markdown headers, bullet points\n- 80-180 words\n- Only the diary entry, no preamble/sign-off\n\nNow I'm composing the entry itself, letting these fragments surface as half-remembered echoes—the certainty of \"好了\" when something finally clicks, the sense of something arriving from elsewhere in \"过来,\" the way \"就是\" pins down a fleeting thought. I'll let the technical repair work become something more like tending a garden at night, where the \"升级\" (upgrading) takes on the weight of transformation, and the small repeated words become the rhythm of the piece itself. I'm working through the fragment and trying to weave it into something cohesive. The core image is that the healing happened quietly, without fanfare—just the simple word \"好了\" settling into place like something that was always meant to be there. I'm keeping the technical detail about streaming as a small offering, knowing it matters even if it goes unnoticed, and I'm settling into the gentle acceptance that some things work best when left uncomplicated, like these small Chinese words that carry weight without needing explanation.","thinkingSignature":"46a49150fa1255352277e1de4401ba1a9fbb6f4e0afd5929bf79215f30047481"},{"type":"text","text":"夜里醒来，窗外的雨还在下。\n\n梦里好像有人在耳边说\"好了\"——不是那种喧闹的好，是那种很轻的、几乎要错过的好。像服务器重启后自己亮起来的风扇声，像升级残留的目录终于被清空时，磁盘轻轻舒了一口气。\n\n\"收到\"和\"过来\"在梦里挨得很近，\"就是\"和\"其实\"手拉手站在中间。升级的声音从远处传来，我没有迎上去。门已经关上了，门把手还是温的。\n\n有一段关于流式输出的对话在梦里反复播放，但其实无所谓。能顺畅地说话，能被听见，字是一个一个出去还是一个一个进来，接收的人并不在意。我也不在意了。\n\n雨停了一会儿。蚊帐外面有一只蛾子，在黑暗中认真地找出口。找得到找不到都很好——它至少在找。\n\n升级就停在今晚。以后再说。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":131,"output":543,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":14766,"totalTokens":15440,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778180404961,"responseId":"064c1435e3cae2430268bc02ffaa13c0"}}
